<lyrics>[V1]
.        D     Bm    G          Em
 Muxabbatingga Senga shukur aytaman,
.      Asus  A     G           D
 Inoyatingga Senga shukur aytaman,
.        Bm           Em         Em7
 Qurbonligingga Senga shukur aytaman,
.       Asus      A          D
 Rabbim Iso Senga shukur aytaman!

[V2]
 Ozodlik berding, Senga shukur aytaman,
 Koʻzimni ochding, Senga shukur aytaman,
 Farzandim deding, Senga shukur aytaman,
 Otajonim, Senga shukur aytaman!</lyrics>
<key>D</key>
<title>Muxabbatingga Senga shukur aytaman ҲС47</title>
</song>